HEADWORD: Sunshade
<hw>Sun"shade`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Anything used as a
protection from the sun's rays.</def> Specifically: <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A
small parasol.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>An awning.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sunshine</ent>⟦br⟧
